content.text:
{
  "message": "Issue created successfully",
  "issue": {
    "id": "27403",
    "key": "DEV-5780",
    "summary": "Admin Role and User Provisioning System",
    "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27403",
    "description": "## Overview\nImplement a comprehensive admin role and user provisioning system that allows administrators to manage users within their tenant, assign roles, and enforce subscription limits.\n\n## Key Features\n- **Role-Based Access Control**: Admin and User roles with proper JWT integration\n- **User Management**: View, add, remove, and manage users within tenant\n- **Subscription Enforcement**: Enforce user limits based on subscription tiers\n- **Admin Interface**: Dedicated admin panel for user and group management\n- **API Security**: Role-based endpoint protection with custom decorators\n\n## Technical Implementation\n- JWT-based role authentication\n- Keycloak/Entra identity management integration\n- NestJS custom role decorators\n- Admin panel UI with user/group management\n- Subscription limit validation\n\n## Questions to Resolve\n- Subscription tier user limits definition\n- Identity provider choice (Keycloak vs Entra)\n- User onboarding process with DSOP/CSMs\n- Initial admin designation for existing customers\n- DEV-3936 branch merge requirements\n\n## Success Criteria\n- Admins can manage all users in their tenant\n- Role assignments work correctly via JWT\n- Subscription limits are enforced\n- Admin panel is intuitive and functional\n- API endpoints are properly secured",
    "status": {
      "name": "Backlog",
      "category": "To Do",
      "color": "blue-gray"
    },
    "issue_type": {
      "name": "Epic"
    },
    "priority": {
      "name": "Lowest"
    },
    "assignee": {
      "display_name": "Unassigned"
    },
    "reporter": {
      "display_name": "Luke O'Malley",
      "name": "Luke O'Malley",
      "email": "luke@procurementsciences.com",
