      "summary": "Implement JWT Role-Based Authentication System",
      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27404",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs a system administrator, I need JWT tokens to include user roles so that the application can enforce role-based access control.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] User roles (Admin, User) are included in JWT tokens\n- [ ] Token generation includes role information from identity provider\n- [ ] Token validation extracts and verifies role claims\n- [ ] Role information is accessible to API endpoints\n- [ ] Existing authentication flow remains intact\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Update JWT token structure to include roles array\n- Integrate with Keycloak/Entra for role retrieval\n- Ensure backward compatibility with existing tokens",
