    {
      "id": "27406",
      "key": "DEV-5783",
      "summary": "Implement User Management API Endpoints",
      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27406",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs an administrator, I need API endpoints to manage users in my tenant so that I can view, create, update, and deactivate user accounts.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] GET /users - List all users in tenant (admin only)\n- [ ] GET /users/{userId} - Get user details (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /users - Create new user with role assignment (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /users/{userId} - Update user details and roles (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /users/{userId}/deactivate - Deactivate user (admin only)\n- [ ] All endpoints protected with @Roles(['admin']) decorator\n- [ ] Proper error handling and validation\n- [ ] Tenant isolation enforced\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Integrate with identity provider for user CRUD operations\n- Validate subscription limits before user creation\n- Include audit logging for user management actions",
      "status": {
