    {
      "id": "27407",
      "key": "DEV-5784",
      "summary": "Implement Group Management API Endpoints",
      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27407",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs an administrator, I need API endpoints to manage groups in my tenant so that I can organize users and manage permissions at scale.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] GET /groups - List all groups (admin only)\n- [ ] GET /groups/{groupId} - Get group details (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /groups - Create new group (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /groups/users/add - Add user to group (admin only)\n- [ ] POST /groups/users/remove - Remove user from group (admin only)\n- [ ] All endpoints protected with @Roles(['admin']) decorator\n- [ ] Proper error handling and validation\n- [ ] Tenant isolation enforced\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Design group structure for future permission expansion\n- Consider group hierarchy if needed\n- Include audit logging for group management actions",
