      "key": "DEV-5785",
      "summary": "Create Admin Panel User Interface",
      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27408",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs an administrator, I need a dedicated admin panel interface so that I can easily manage users and groups within my tenant.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Admin panel accessible from side navigation (admin role only)\n- [ ] User management page with list view of all tenant users\n- [ ] User details modal/page with role assignment controls\n- [ ] Group management page with group creation and member management\n- [ ] Responsive design that works on desktop and tablet\n- [ ] Loading states and error handling for all operations\n- [ ] Confirmation dialogs for destructive actions\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Add admin panel route to side navigation\n- Create reusable components for user/group management\n- Implement proper state management for admin operations\n- Follow existing UI/UX patterns and design system",
