      "key": "DEV-5787",
      "summary": "Integrate with Identity Provider (Keycloak/Entra)",
      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27410",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs a system, I need to integrate with the chosen identity provider so that user and role management is centralized and secure.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Determine identity provider choice (Keycloak vs Entra)\n- [ ] Configure identity provider for role management\n- [ ] Implement user CRUD operations via identity provider APIs\n- [ ] Sync user roles between identity provider and application\n- [ ] Handle identity provider errors gracefully\n- [ ] Maintain existing authentication flows\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Research current identity provider setup\n- Implement provider-specific API integrations\n- Create abstraction layer for future provider changes\n- Update token validation to use provider roles\n\n## Dependencies\n- Requires decision on identity provider choice\n- May need identity provider configuration changes",
