      "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27411",
      "description": "## User Story\nAs a system administrator, I need a process to designate initial admin users so that new and existing tenants have proper administrative access.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Process for new customers during onboarding\n- [ ] Process for existing customers via CSM outreach\n- [ ] Admin user designation API/interface for CSMs\n- [ ] Validation to ensure at least one admin per tenant\n- [ ] Documentation for CSM admin setup process\n- [ ] Audit logging for admin role assignments\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Create CSM tools for admin designation\n- Implement tenant admin validation rules\n- Consider emergency admin access procedures\n- Integration with onboarding workflows\n\n## Questions to Resolve\n- Specific onboarding integration points?\n- CSM tool requirements and access levels?\n- Emergency admin access procedures?",
