    "description": "## User Story\nAs a developer, I need a reusable decorator to protect API endpoints with role-based access control so that only authorized users can access specific functionality.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] @Roles decorator accepts array of required roles\n- [ ] Decorator validates JWT token roles against required roles\n- [ ] Returns 403 Forbidden for insufficient permissions\n- [ ] Works with existing authentication middleware\n- [ ] Includes comprehensive error handling\n\n## Example Usage\n```typescript\n@GET('users')\n@Roles(['admin', 'proposal_writer'])\nfunction getUsers() {\n  return []\n}\n```",
